sentences.english: At the end of the term, you typically get no cash back.
sentences.chinese: 固定年限到期后，你一般不会得到任何现金返还。

sentences.english: If you have insurance under a student plan, it probably will end in mid-August.
sentences.chinese: 如果你买的是学生险，保险可能会在八月中旬到期。

sentences.english: The restraining order had expired that day.
The plaintiff loaned the defendant money, and the defendant failed to repay it.
sentences.chinese: 原告借给被告钱，被告到期不能偿还。

sentences.english: The former Manchester United player's contract with Los Angeles Galaxy runs out at the end of December.
sentences.chinese: 前曼联球星与洛杉矶银河队的合同12底就将到期。

sentences.english: The new rules will kick in when the bloc's existing regulation on mobile roaming expires at the end of June next year.
sentences.chinese: 新规定将在明年六月底现行规则到期后开始实施。

sentences.english: My regular deposit is ended today ,may I continue ?
sentences.chinese: 我的定期存款今天到期，我可以续存吗？

sentences.english: You have to renew the contract to continue own the shop.
sentences.chinese: 你需要在租期到期之前续租以继续开店。

sentences.english: He noticed that Ye was grabbing his expired names with lightning speed.
sentences.chinese: 他注意，叶云以闪电般速度抢注了他拥有的到期域名。

sentences.english: Though the Plaintiff has repeatedly demanded the payment, the Defendant fails to liquidate the outstanding debts in due time.
sentences.chinese: 尽管原告多次催讨货款，被告仍未能清偿到期债务。

sentences.english: The bills came due, and we're still paying the price today.
sentences.chinese: 各种票据纷纷到期，迄今我们还在为此付出代价。

sentences.english: People who owe comparatively large amount of debt which is overdue.
sentences.chinese: 个人所负数额较大的债务到期未清偿的。

sentences.english: All links must be on-page PR, not domain PR.
sentences.chinese: 友情链接必须是永久的，积极的，从来没有到期。

sentences.english: Its mandate is due to expire next month, but it is expected to be renewed. 0 M7 V% V.
sentences.chinese: 联合国在那里的维和使命本月到期，但预计会延长。

sentences.english: Fed Governor Warsh is will step down on March 31.
sentences.chinese: 美联储官员瓦尔许任期将于3月31日到期。
